  "texts": [
    "There was a total of forty-five (45) Grade-10 Junior High School learners catered in this study and random sampling technique was utilized to ensure the reliability and validity of the study.",
    "The process of data gathering started though securing a written permission through channels in order to obtain full cooperation from respondents.",
    "As soon as the permission was granted, the researchers set the schedules for the conduct of survey and written test in the Grade-10 class.",
    "A survey questionnaire was utilized to gather the data of the respondents.",
    "It consists of two parts."
